Package NoninPackage

Interface Summary
INoninListener Must be implemented by all classes that want to get and deal with the Nonin events.
 

Class Summary
NoninData Contains all Nonin data excluding the O2 and pulse data.
NoninDiscoveryListener Contains all necessary logic to discover the Nonin via BlueTooth
NoninEvent Defines the Nonin event.
NoninManager Manages the Nonin connection and the throwing event logic.
